Introduction

Lim Haram, known under her stage name Hana, is a South Korean singer, dancer, and composer under ATTRAKT. She is best known as the main vocalist and sub rapper of the girl group FIFTY FIFTY.

Before debuting, Hana was a contestant on the survival show WE KID where she sung the little mermaid OST "Part of Your World" in episode 3.

On June 22, 2020, Hana made her solo debut, with the digital single "Secret Crush".

On August 12, 2024, Hana was the third member of FIFTY FIFTY to be revealed. She later made her group debut on August 30, 2024, with the group's pre-release single "Starry Night".
